These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different games are played: poker, domino, go, canasta
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, rugby, tennis
1. the person playing go is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is rowing##2
2. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
3. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
4. the person who's sport is rowing is not the person playing go##6
5. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
6. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Game   | canasta  | poker | go | domino  |
| Sport   | biathlon | rugby   | tennis  | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, american, thai, argentine
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, journalist, nurse, project-manager
1. the project-manager is not to the left of the project-manager##8
2. the italian is somewhere to the right of the argentine##5
3. the italian is the journalist##1
4. the argentine is between the italian and the american##2
5. the american is somewhere between the thai and the designer##7
6. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the american##5
7. the designer is not to the left of the designer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | thai | american          | argentine | italian     |
| Job    | nurse      | project-manager | designer | journalist |

