.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, march, june, august
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, family, superhero
1. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##8
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
7. the person who's birthday is in august is the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Birthday           | july | march | june     | august |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | superhero   | adventure | family    |

