.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, disco, metal, rock
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, tram, snowmobile, helicopter
1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the fan of disco##1
4. the fan of rock is not to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##8
5. the fan of blues is the person driving the bus##1
6. the fan of blues is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
7. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | disco         | rock   | blues    |
| Transport         | tram | helicopter | snowmobile | bus |

