.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
House: wooden, colonial, ranch-style, palace
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, handball, rugby
1. the palace house is somewhere between the wooden house and the colonial house##7
2. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
3. the palace house is somewhere between the ranch-style house and the wooden house##7
4. the ranch-style house is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
5. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the colonial house and the person who's sport is cycling##7
6. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the palace house##5
7. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the wooden house##8
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the palace house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| House   | colonial   | ranch-style | palace | wooden    |
| Sport         | climbing | rugby   | handball   | cycling |

