.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, kiwi, lettuce, pineapple
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, rowing, badminton, cycling
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the person eating cauliflower##5
3. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
5. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
6. the person eating pineapple is not to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##8
7. the person eating pineapple is the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | pineapple | cauliflower | kiwi  | lettuce |
| Sport   | rowing   | cycling         | badminton | tennis |

