.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, sprite, water
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, march, april, september
1. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
2. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person who's birthday is in april##7
3. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5
4. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##8
5. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | cola      | sprite | almond-milk | water   |
| Birthday      | august | april | september  | march |

