2. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
5. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the person watching animation movies##8
6. the person watching animation movies is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person watching adventure movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Movie-Genre     | martial-arts | adventure | animation | scientific     |
| Sport   | baseball   | rugby        | tennis          | ice-hockey |

