5. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the fan of indie is not the person who's sport is basketball##6
7. the fan of pop is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
8. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the left of the person who's sport is handball##8

