2. the person driving the airplane is not the person traveling to colone##6
3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is not to the right of the person traveling to prague##8
5. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| City         | hannover | prague      | san-francisco   | colone  |
| Transport   | taxi    | motorbike | airplane | snowmobile |

