5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
6. the british is somewhere between the japanese and the person drinking fanta##7
7. the british is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | fanta         | juice    | cola       |
| Nationality      | american | pakistani | british | japanese |

