.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, hamster, hedgehog
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, alhambra, chaman, blend
1. the alhambra-smoker is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
2. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the blend-smoker##8
4. the owner of the hamster is the dannemann-smoker##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the alhambra-smoker and the dannemann-smoker##7
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the chaman-smoker is between the blend-smoker and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | frog    | hedgehog | chinchilla | hamster |
| Cigar   | alhambra | blend      | chaman     | dannemann     |

 